Modular build script: Add nacl-glibc build

Add Git support via GitTree object.

Add ability to use install_root instead of DESTDIR for "make install",
since glibc doesn't support DESTDIR.

Add a nacl-glibc build step.

Add the ability to build a subset of targets, since the final step
(testing building an executable with the nacl-glibc toolchain) does
not work yet.

